snippet: The University of Minnesota football team on Saturday said it would not boycott its upcoming bowl game this month to protest the suspension of 10 players in connection with a sexual assault investigation....
lead_paragraph: The University of Minnesota football team on Saturday said it would not boycott its upcoming bowl game this month to protest the suspension of 10 players in connection with a sexual assault investigation.

headline.main: University of Minnesota Football Team Cancels Boycott Over Sex Assault Suspensions
headline.print_headline: University of Minnesota Football Team Cancels Boycott Over Sex Assault Suspensions
